title: Accommodation in rafraf beach
feedBack: Honestly it was lot better than what I expected. It was close to everything and restaurants are less than a minute away. I had my privacy. It was 10mins walk to the medina, and close to the metro too. I stayed for 12days so the washing machine was very useful. Fully working stove, I cooked at home sometimes. Checkin and checkout was hassle free, even though I spoke no Arabic or French. One day I locked myself out and Mohamed was very kind to come to open the door for me. He is a proper gentleman. I will definitely recommend his place, and I will stay again
